quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  16,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  16,1,khuda ka hukum ( yani azaab goya ) aa hi pouncha to ( kafroo ) is ke liye jaldi mat karo. yeh log jo ( khuda ka ) shareek banatay hain woh is se pak aur balatar hai
  16,2,wohi firshton ko pegham day kar apne hukum se apne bundon mein se jis ke paas chahta hai bhejta hai ke ( logon ko ) btado ke mere siwa koi mabood nahi to mujhi se daro
  16,3,isi ne asmano aur zameen ko mabni bar hikmat pedakiya. is ki zaat un ( kafiroon ) ke shirk se onche hai
  16,4,isi ne ensaan ko nutfay se banaya magar woh is ( khaaliq ) ke baray mein alania jhagrnay laga
  16,5,aur charpayon ko bhi isi ne pedakiya. un mein tumahray liye jarrawal (Khobsorti ) aur bohat se faiday hain aur un mein se baaz ko tum khatay bhi ho
  16,6,aur jab shaam ko inhen ( jungle se ) laatay ho aur jab subah ko ( jungle ) churanay le jatay ho to un se tumhari izzat o shan hai
  16,7,aur ( daur daraaz ) shehron mein jahan tum Zahmat shaqeh ke baghair poanch nahi satke woh tumahray boojh utha kar le jatay hain. kuch shak nahi ke tumhara perwar-digaar nihayat shafqat wala aur meharban hai
  16,8,aur isi ne ghoray aur khachar aur gadhay peda kiye taakay tum un par sawaar ho aur ( woh tumahray liye ) ronaqe o zinat ( bhi hain ) aur woh ( aur cheeze bhi ) peda karta hai jin ki tum ko khabar nahi
  16,9,aur seedha rasta to khuda taq ja pohanchana hai. aur baaz raste tirhhe hain ( woh is taq nahi pahunchte ) aur agar woh chahta to tum sab ko seedhay raste par chala deta
  16,10,wohi to hai jis ne aasman se pani barsaya jisay tum peetay ho aur is se darakht bhi ( shadaab hotay hain ) jin mein tum apne charpayon ko churatay ho
  16,11,isi pani se woh tumahray liye khaiti aur Zaitoon aur khajoor aur angoor ( aur be shumaar darakht ) ugata hai. aur har terhan ke phal ( peda karta hai ) ghhor karne walon ke liye is mein ( qudrat khuda ki barri ) nishani hai
  16,12,aur isi ne tumahray liye raat aur din aur Sooraj aur chaand ko kaam mein lagaya. aur isi ke hukum se setaaray bhi kaam mein lagey hue hain. samajhney walon ke liye is mein ( qudrat khuda ki bohat si ) nishanain hain
  16,13,aur jo terhan terhan ke rangon ki cheeze is ne zameen mein peda kee ( sab tumahray zair farmaan kar dein ) nasiyaat pakarney walon ke liye is mein nishani hai
  16,14,aur wohi to hai jis ne darya ko tumahray ikhtiyar meinkiya taakay is mein se taaza gosht khao aur is se zewar ( moti waghera ) nikalu jisay tum pehantay ho. aur tum dekhte ho ke kashtiyan darya mein pani ko phatri chali jati hain. aur is liye bhi ( darya ko tumahray ikhtiyar meinkiya ) ke tum khuda ke fazl se ( muaash ) talaash karo taakay is ka shukar karo
  16,15,aur isi ne zameen par pahar ( bana kar ) rakh diye ke tum ko le kar kahin jhuk nah jaye aur nehrain aur raste bana diye taakay aik maqam se dosray maqam taq ( aasani se ) jaa sako
  16,16,aur ( raastoon mein ) nishanaat bana diye aur log sitaron se bhi raste maloom karte hain
  16,17,to jo ( itni makhloqaat ) peda kere.kiya woh waisa hai jo kuch bhi peda nah kar sakay to phir tum ghhor kyun nahi karte ?
  16,18,aur agar tum khuda ki nematon ko shumaar karna chaho to gun nah sakuu. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  16,19,aur jo kuch tum chupatay aur jo kuch zahir karte ho sab se khuda waaqif hai
  16,20,aur jin logon ko yeh khuda ke siwa pkarte hain woh koi cheez bhi to nahi bnaskte balkay khud un ko aur banatay hain
  16,21,lashain hain be jaan. un ko yeh bhi to maloom nahi ke uthaye kab jayen ge
  16,22,tumhara mabood to akela khuda hai. to jo akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay un ke dil inkaar kar rahay hain aur woh sarkash ho rahay hain
  16,23,yeh jo kuch chupatay hain aur jo zahir karte hain khuda is ko zaroor jaanta hai. woh sarkashon ko hargiz pasand nahi karta
  16,24,aur jab un ( kafiroon ) se kaha jata hai ke tumahray perwar-digaar nekiya utaara hai to kehte hain ke ( woh to ) pehlay logon ki hikaytein hain
  16,25,( ae paighambar un ko bikny do ) yeh qayamat ke din apne ( aamaal ke ) poooray boojh bhi utthayen ge aur jin ko yeh be tahaqeeq gumraah karte hain un ke boojh bhi utthayen ge. sun rakho ke jo boojh utha rahay hain buray hain
  16,26,un se pehlay logon ne bhi ( aisi hi )makaryan ki theen to khuda ( ka hukum ) un ki imarat ke satonon par aap_hncha aur chhat un par un ke oopar se gir pari aur ( aisi taraf se ) un par azaab aa waqay howa jahan se un ko khayaal bhi nah tha
  16,27,phir woh un ko qayamat ke din bhi zaleel kere ga aur kahe ga ke mere woh shareek kahan hain jin ke baray mein tum jhagra karte they. jin logon ko ilm diya gaya tha woh kahin ge ke aaj kafiroon ki ruswai aur buraiee hai
  16,28,( un ka haal yeh hai ke ) jab farishtay un ki roohein qabz karne lagtay hain ( aur yeh ) apne hi haq mein zulm karne walay ( hotay hain ) to Mutee o munhqad (hatyar dal dayte hain) ho jatay hain ( aur kehte hain ) ke hum koi bura kaam nahi karte they. haan jo kuch tumkiya karte they khuda usay khoob jaanta hai
  16,29,so dozakh ke darwazon mein daakhil hojao. hamesha is mein raho ge. ab taqqabur karne walon ka bura thikana hai
  16,30,aur ( jab ) parhaiz garon se poocha jata hai ke tumahray perwar-digaar nekiya nazilkiya hai. to kehte hain ke behtareen ( kalaam ). jo log nekokaar hain un ke liye is duniya mein bhalai hai. aur akhirat ka ghar to bohat hi acha hai. aur parhaiz gaaron ka ghar bohat khoob hai
  16,31,( woh ) bahisht javedani ( hain ) jin mein woh daakhil hon ge un ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain wahan jo chahain ge un ke liye muyassar hoga. khuda parhaiz garon ko aisa hi badla deta hai
  16,32,( un ki kefiyat yeh hai ke ) jab farishtay un ki jaanen nikaalte lagtay hain aur yeh ( kufar o shirk se ) pak hotay hain to salam alaikum kehte hain ( aur kehte hain ke ) jo amal tumkiya karte they un ke badlay mein bahisht mein daakhil hojao
  16,33,kiya yeh ( kafir ) is baat ke munhtazir hain ke farishtay un ke paas ( jaan nikaalte ) ayen ya tumahray perwar-digaar ka hukum ( azaab ) aa pohnchay. isi terhan unn logon nekiya tha jo unn se pehlay they aur khuda ne unn par zulm nahikiya balkay woh khud apne aap par zulm karte they
  16,34,to un ko un ke aamaal ke buray badlay miley aur jis cheez ke sath woh thathaykiya karte they is ne un ko ( har taraf se ) ghair liya
  16,35,aur mushriq kehte hain ke agar khuda chahta to nah hum hi is ke siwa kisi cheez ko pujte aur nah hamaray barray hi ( pujte ) aur nah is ke ( farmaan ke ) baghair hum kisi cheez ko haraam th_hrate. ( ae paighambar ) isi terhan un se aglay logon nekiya tha. to payghambaroon ke zimmay ( khuda ke ehkaam ko ) khol kar suna dainay ke siwa aur kuch nahi
  16,36,aur hum ne har jamaat mein paighambar bheja ke khuda hi ki ibadat karo aur buton ( ki parastish ) se ijtinab karo. to un mein baaz aisay hain jin ko khuda ne hadaayat di aur baaz aisay hain jin par gumraahi saabit hui. so zameen par chal phir kar dekh lau ke jhutlanay walon ka injaam kaisa howa
  16,37,agar tum un ( kufar ) ki hadaayat ke liye lalchao to jis ko khuda gumraah kardaita hai is ko woh hadaayat nahi diya karta aur aisay logon ka koi madadgaar bhi nahi hota
  16,38,aur yeh khuda ki sakht sakht kasmain khatay hain ke jo mrjata hai khuda usay ( qayamat ke din qabar se ) nahi uthaye ga. hargiz nahi. yeh ( khuda ka ) wada sacha hai aur is ka poora karna usay zaroor hai lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  16,39,taakay jin baton mein yeh ikhtilaaf karte hain woh un par zahir kardey aur is liye ke kafir jaan len ke woh jhutay they
  16,40,jab hum kisi cheez ka iradah karte hain to hamari baat yahi hai ke is ko keh dete hain ke hoja to woh hojati hai
  16,41,aur jin logon ne zulm sehney ke baad khuda ke liye watan chorra hum un ko duniya mein acha thikana den ge. aur akhirat ka ajar to bohat bara hai. kash woh ( usay ) jantay
  16,42,yani woh log jo sabr karte hain aur apne perwar-digaar par bhrosa rakhtay hain
  16,43,aur hum ne tum se pehlay mardon hi ko paighambar bana kar bheja tha jin ki taraf hum wahi bheja karte they agar tum log nahi jantay to ahal kitaab se pooch lau
  16,44,( aur un payghambaroon ko ) daleelen aur kitaaben day kar ( bheja tha ) aur hum ne tum par bhi yeh kitaab nazil ki hai taakay jo ( arshadat ) logon par nazil hue hain woh un par zahir kardo aur taakay woh ghhor karen
  16,45,kiya jo log buri buri chaalein chaltay hain is baat se be khauf hain ke khuda un ko zameen mein dhansa day ya ( aisi taraf se ) un par azaab aajay jahan se un ko khabar hi nah ho
  16,46,ya un ko chaltay phirtay pakar le woh ( khuda ko ) aajiz nahi kar saktay
  16,47,ya jab un ko azaab ka dar peda hogaya ho to un ko pkrhle. be shak tumhara perwar-digaar bohat shafqat karne wala aur meharban hai
  16,48,kiya un logon ne khuda ki makhloqaat mein se aisi cheeze nahi dekhen jin ke saaye dayen se ( baen ko ) aur baen se ( dayen ko ) lottay rehtay hain ( yani ) khuda ke agay aajiz ho kar sjday mein parre rehtay hain
  16,49,aur tamam jandaar jo asmano mein hain aur jo zameen mein hain sab khuda ke agay sajda karte hain aur farishtay bhi aur woh zara ghuroor nahi karte
  16,50,aur apne perwar-digaar se jo un ke oopar hai drtay hain aur jo un ko irshad hota hai is par amal karte hain
  16,51,aur khuda ne farmaya hai ke do do mabood nah banaao. mabood wohi aik hai. to mujh hi se drtay raho
  16,52,aur jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab isi ka hai aur isi ki ibadat lazim hai. to tum khuda ke siwa ouron se kyun drtay ho
  16,53,aur jo naematain tum ko muyassar hain sab khuda ki taraf se hain. phir jab tum ko koi takleef pahunchti hai to isi ke agay chillate ho
  16,54,phir jab woh tum se takleef ko daur kardaita hai to kuch log tum mein se khuda ke sath shareek karne lagtay hain
  16,55,taakay jo ( naematain ) hum ne un ko ataa farmai hain un ki nashukri karen to ( mushrako ) duniya mein faiday utha loo . anqareeb tum ko ( is ka injaam ) maloom hojaye ga
  16,56,aur hamaray diye hue maal mein se aisi cheezon ka hissa muqarrar karte hain jin ko jantay hi nahi. ( kafroo ) khuda ki qasam ke jo tum iftira karte ho is ki tum se zaroor prssh hogi
  16,57,aur yeh log khuda ke liye to betiyan tajweez karte hain. ( aur ) woh un se pak hai aur apne liye ( betay ) jo Marghoob o dil pasand hain
  16,58,halaank jab un mein se kisi ko beti ( ke peda honay ) ki khabar millti hai to is ka munh ( gham ke sabab ) kala par jata hai aur ( is ke dil ko dekho to ) woh andohnak hojata hai
  16,59,aur is khabar bad se ( jo woh santa hai ) logon se chupta phirta hai ( aur sochta hai ) ke aaya zillat bardasht karkay larki ko zindah rehne day ya zameen mein garh day. dekho yeh jo tajweez karte hain bohat buri hai
  16,60,jo log akhirat par imaan nahi rakhtay un hi ke liye buri baatein ( Shayan ) hain. aur khuda ko sift aala ( Zaib deti hai ) aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  16,61,aur agar khuda logon ko un ke zulm ke sabab pakarney lagey to aik jandaar ko zameen par nah chhorey lekin un ko aik waqt muqarrar taq mohlat diye jata hai. jab woh waqt ajata hai to aik gharri nah peechay reh satke hain nah agay barh satke hain
  16,62,aur yeh khuda ke liye aisi cheeze tajweez karte hain jin ko khud napasand karte hain aur zabaan se jhoot bikey jatay hain ke un ko ( qayamat ke din ) bhalai ( yani nijaat ) hogi. kuch shak nahi ke un ke liye ( dozakh ki ) aag ( tayyar ) hai aur yeh ( dozakh mein ) sab se agay beje jayen ge
  16,63,khuda ki qasam hum ne tum se pehli amton ki taraf bhi paighambar beje to shetan ne un ke kirdaar ( na shaista ) un ko aaraasta kar dukhaay to aaj bhi wohi un ka dost hai aur un ke liye azaab alim hai
  16,64,aur hum ne jo tum par kitaab nazil ki hai to is ke liye jis amar mein un logon ko ikhtilaaf hai tum is ka faisla kardo. aur ( yeh ) mominoun ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
  16,65,aur khuda hi ne aasman se pani barsaya phir is se zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad zindahkiya. be shak is mein suneney walon ke liye nishani hai
  16,66,aur tumahray liye charpayon mein bhi ( maqam ) Ibrat (o ghor ) hai ke un ke piton mein jo gobar aur lahoo hai is se hum tum ko khalis doodh pilate hain jo peenay walon ke liye Khushgawar hai
  16,67,aur khajoor aur angoor ke mewon se bhi ( tum peenay ki cheeze tayyar karte ho ke un se sharaab banatay ho ) aur umdah rizaq ( khatay ho ) jo log samajh rakhtay hain un ke liye un ( cheezon ) mein ( qudrat khuda ki ) nishani hai
  16,68,aur tumahray perwar-digaar ne shehad ki makhion ko irshad farmaya ke pahoron mein aur darakhton mein aur onche onche chatriyon mein jo log banatay hain ghar bana
  16,69,aur har qasam ke meway kha. aur apne perwar-digaar ke saaf rustoon par chali ja. is ke pait se peenay ki cheez nikalti hai jis ke mukhtalif rang hotay hain is mein logon ( ke kayi amraaz ) ki Shifa hai. be shak sochnay walon ke liye is mein bhi nishani hai
  16,70,aur khuda hi ne tum ko pedakiya. phir wohi tum ko mout deta hai aur tum mein baaz aisay hotay hain ke nihayat kharab Umar ko poanch jatay hain aur ( bohat kuch ) jan-nay ke baad har cheez se be ilm ho jatay hain. be shak khuda ( sab kuch ) jan-nay wala ( aur ) qudrat wala hai
  16,71,aur khuda ne rizaq ( o dolat ) mein baaz ko baaz par fazeelat di hai to jin logon ko fazeelat di hai woh apna rizaq apne mamlokon ko to de daalnay walay hain nahi ke sab is mein barabar ho jaien. tokiya yeh log Nemat Ellahi ke munhkir hain
  16,72,aur khuda hi ne tum mein se tumahray liye aurtain peda kee aur aurton se tumahray betay aur potay peda kiye aur khanay ko tumhe pakeeza cheeze den. tokiya be asal cheezon par aitqaad rakhtay aur khuda ki nematon se inkaar karte hain
  16,73,aur khuda ke siwa aison ko pujte hain jo un ko asmano aur zameen mein rozi dainay ka zara bhi ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay aur nah kisi aur terhan ka Maqdoor rakhtay hain
  16,74,to ( logo ) khuda ke baray mein ( ghalat ) misalein nah banaao. ( sahih misalon ka tareeqa ) khuda hi jaanta hai aur tum nahi jantay
  16,75,khuda aik aur misaal bayan farmata hai ke aik ghulam hai jo ( bilkul ) dosray ke ikhtiyar mein hai aur kisi cheez par qudrat nahi rakhta aur aik aisa shakhs hai jis ko hum ne apne haan se ( bohat sa ) maal Tayyab ataa farmaya hai aur woh is mein se ( raat din ) posheeda aur zahir kharch karta rehta hai tokiya yeh dono shakhs barabar hain? ( hargiz nahi ) Al Hamdo Lillah lekin un mein se aksar log nahi samajh rakhtay
  16,76,aur khuda aik aur misaal bayan farmata hai ke do aadmi hain aik unn mein se goonga ( aur dosray ki malik ) hai ( be ikhtiyar o natawan ) ke kisi cheez par qudrat nahi rakhta. aur apne maalik ko dobhr ho raha hai woh jahan ussay bhejta hai ( kher se kabhi ) bhalai nahi lata.kiya aisa ( goonga berha ) aur woh shakhs jo ( santa boltaa aur ) logon ko insaaf karne ka hukum deta hai aur khud seedhay rastay par chal raha hai dono barabar hain ?
  16,77,aur asmano aur zameen ka ilm khuda hi ko hai aur ( khuda ke nazdeek ) qayamat ka aana yun hai jaisay aankhh ka jhapakna balkay is se bhi jald tar. kuch shak nahi ke khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  16,78,aur khuda hi ne tum ko tumhari maaon ke shikam se pedakiya ke tum kuch nahi jantay they. aur is ne tum ko kaan aur ankhen aur dil ( aur unn ke ilawa aur ) aaza bakhshay taakay tum shukar karo
  16,79,kiya un logon ne parindon ko nahi dekha ke aasman ki howa mein ghiry hue ( urtye rehtay ) hain. un ko khuda hi thaamay rakhta hai. imaan walon ke liye is mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  16,80,"aur khuda hi ne tumahray liye gharon ko rehne ki jagah banaya aur usi ne chopaiyon ki khaalon se tumahray liye daairay banaye. jin ko tum subk dekh kar safar aur Hazr mein kaam mein laatay ho aur unn ki oon, pasham aur balon se tum asbaab aur baratnay ki cheeze ( banatay ho jo ) muddat taq ( kaam deti hain )"
  16,81,aur khuda hi ne tumahray ( aaraam ke ) liye apni peda ki hui cheezon ke saaye banaye aur pahoron mein غاریں banayen aur karte banaye jo tum ko garmi se bachayen. aur ( aisay ) karte ( bhi ) jo tum ko asleha jung ( ke zarrar ) se mehfooz rakhen. isi terhan khuda apna ahsaan tum par poora karta hai taakay tum farmanbardar bano
  16,82,aur agar yeh log aitraaz karen to ( ae paighambar ) tumhara kaam faqat khol kar suna dena hai
  16,83,yeh khuda ki nematon se waaqif hain. magar ( waaqif ho kar ) unn se inkaar karte hain aur yeh aksar nashukray hain
  16,84,aur jis din hum har aُmt mein se gawah ( yani paighambar ) khara karen ge to nah to kufar ko ( bolnay ki ) ijazat miley gi aur nah unn ke izr qubool kiye jayen ge
  16,85,aur jab zalim log azaab dekh len ge to phir nah to unn ke azaab hi mein takhfeef ki jaye gi aur nah unn ko mohlat hi di jaye gi
  16,86,aur jab mushriq ( apne banaye hue ) sharikon ko dekhen ge to kahin ge ke perwar-digaar yeh wohi hamaray shareek hain jin ko hum tairay siwa pُkara karte they. to woh ( unn ke kalaam ko mustard kar dein ge aur ) unn se kahin ge ke tum to jhutay ho
  16,87,aur is din khuda ke samnay surangoon ho jayen ge aur jo tufaan woh baandha karte they sab unn se jata rahay ga
  16,88,jin logon ne kufarkiya aur ( logon ko ) khuda ke raste se roka hum unn ko azaab par azaab den ge. is liye ke shararatkiya karte they
  16,89,aur ( is din ko yaad karo ) jis din hum har aُmt mein se khud unn par gawah kharray karen ge. aur ( ae paighambar ) tum ko un logon par gawah layein ge. aur hum ne tum par ( aisi ) kitaab nazil ki hai ke ( is mein ) har cheez ka bayan ( mufasil ) hai aur musalmanoon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat aur basharat hai
  16,90,khuda tum ko insaaf aur ahsaan karne aur rishta daaron ko ( kharch se madad ) dainay ka hukum deta hai. aur be hiyai aur namaqool kamon se aur sar kashi se mana karta hai ( aur ) tumhe nasiyaat karta hai taakay tum yaad rakho
  16,91,aur jab khuda se ehad wasiq karo to is ko poora karo aur jab paki kasmain khao to unn ko mat torro ke tum khuda ko apna zamin muqarrar kar chukay ho. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is ko jaanta hai
  16,92,aur uss aurat ki terhan nah hona jis ne mehnat se to soot kata. phir is ko toar kar tukre tukre kar dala. ke tum apni qasmon ko aapas mein is baat ka zareya bananay lagu ke aik giroh dosray giroh se ziyada ghalib rahay. baat yeh hai ke khuda tumhe is se aazmata hai. aur jin baton mein tum ikhtilaaf karte ho qayamat ko is ki haqeeqat tum par zahir kar day ga
  16,93,aur agar khuda chahta to tum ( sab ) ko aik hi jamaat bana deta. lekin woh jisay chahta hai gumraah karta hai aur jisay chahta hai hadaayat deta hai. aur jo amal tum karte ho ( uss din ) unn ke baray mein tum se zaroor poocha jaye ga
  16,94,aur apni qasmon ko aapas mein is baat ka zareya nah banaao ke ( logon ke ) qadam jim chikane ke baad lar khara jayen aur is wajah se ke tum ne logon ko khuda ke raste se roka tum ko uqobat ka maza chakhna parre. aur bara sakht azaab miley
  16,95,aur khuda se jo tum ne ehadkiya hai ( is ko mat bechoo aur ) is ke badlay thori si qeemat nah lau. ( kyunkay ayfaye ehad ka ) jo sila khuda ke haan muqarrar hai woh agar samjhoo to tumahray liye behtar hai
  16,96,jo kuch tumahray paas hai woh khatam ho jata hai aur jo khuda ke paas hai woh baqi hai ke ( kabhi khatam nahi hoga ) aur jin logon ne sabrkiya hum unn ko un ke aamaal ka bohat acha badla den ge
  16,97,jo shakhs naik aamaal kere ga mard ho ya aurat woh momin bhi hoga to hum is ko ( duniya mein ) pak ( aur aaraam ki ) zindagi se zindah rakhen ge aur ( akhirat mein ) unn ke aamaal ka nihayat acha sila den ge
  16,98,aur jab tum quran parhnay lagu to shetan mardood se panah maang liya karo
  16,99,ke jo momin hain apne perwar-digaar par bharosa rakhtay hain unn par is ka kuch zor nahi chalta
  16,100,is ka zor un hi logon par chalta hai jo is ko Rafeeq banatay hain aur is ke ( was wasay ke ) sabab ( khuda ke sath ) shareek muqarrar karte hain
  16,101,aur jab hum koi aayat kisi aayat ki jagah badal dete hain. aur khuda jo kuch nazil farmata hai usay khoob jaanta hai to ( kafir ) kehte hain ke tum yuhin apni taraf se bana laatay ho. haqeeqat yeh hai ke un mein aksar nadaan hain
  16,102,keh do ke is ko rooh al quds tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se sachaai ke sath le kar nazil hue hain taakay yeh ( quran ) mominoun ko saabit qadam rakhay aur hukum maan-ne walon ke liye to ( yeh ) hadaayat aur basharat hai
  16,103,aur hamein maloom hai ke yeh kehte hain ke is ( paighambar ) ko 1 shakhs sikha jata hai. magar jis ki taraf ( taleem ki ) nisbat karte hain is ki zabaan to ajmi hai aur yeh saaf arabi zabaan hai
  16,104,yeh log khuda ki aayton par imaan nahi laatay un ko khuda hadaayat nahi deta aur un ke liye azaab alim hai
  16,105,jhoot iftira to wohi logkiya karte hain jo khuda ki aayton par imaan nahi laatay. aur wohi jhutay hain
  16,106,jo shakhs imaan laane ke baad khuda ke sath kufar kere woh nahi jo ( kufar par zabardasti ) majaboorkiya jaye aur is ka dil imaan ke sath mutmaen ho. balkay woh jo ( dil se aur ) dil khol kar kufar kere. to aison par allah ka ghazab hai. aur un ko bara sakht azaab hoga
  16,107,yeh is liye ke unhon ne duniya ki zindagi ko akhirat ke muqablay mein Aziz rakha. aur is liye khuda kafir logon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  16,108,yahi log hain jin ke dilon par aur kaanon par aur aankhon par khuda ne mohar laga rakhi hai. aur yahi ghaflat mein parre hue hain
  16,109,kuch shak nahi ke yeh akhirat mein khasara uthany walay hon ge
  16,110,phir jin logon ne eza-ayn uthany ke baad tark watankiya. phir jehaad kiye aur saabit qadam rahay tumhara perwar-digaar un ko be shak un ( aazmayshon ) ke baad bakhsnay wala ( aur un par ) rehmat karne wala hai
  16,111,jis din har mutnaqas apni taraf se jhagra karne aeye ga. aur har shakhs ko is ke aamaal ka poora poora badla diya jaye ga. aur kisi ka nuqsaan nahikiya jaye ga
  16,112,aur khuda aik bastii ki misaal bayan farmata hai ke ( har terhan ) aman chain se bastii thi har taraf se rizaq ba fraghat chala aata tha. magar un logon ne khuda ki nematon ki nashukri ki to khuda ne un ke aamaal ke sabab un ko bhook aur khauf ka libaas pehna kar ( nashukri ka ) maza chakkha diya
  16,113,aur un ke paas un hi mein se aik paighambar aaya to unhon ne is ko jhtlaya so un ko azaab ne aapkrha aur woh zalim they
  16,114,pas khuda ne jo tum ko halal tayyab rizaq diya hai usay khao. aur allah ki nematon ka shukar karo. agar isi ki ibadat karte ho
  16,115,is ne tum par Murdaar aur lahoo aur soor ka gosht haraam kardiya hai aur jis cheez par khuda ke siwa kisi aur ka naam puraka jaye ( is ko bhi ) haan agar koi nachar hojaye to bashart e kay gunah karne wala nah ho aur nah hadd se niklny wala to khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  16,116,aur yun hi jhoot jo tumhari zabaan par aajay mat keh diya karo ke yeh halal hai aur yeh haraam hai ke khuda par jhoot bohtan bandhnay lagu. jo log khuda par jhoot bohtan bandhtay hain un ka bhala nahi hoga
  16,117,( jhoot ka ) faida to thora sa hai magar ( is ke badlay ) un ko azaab alim bohat hoga
  16,118,aur cheeze hum tum se pehlay bayan kar chukay hain woh hum ne yahudion par haraam kar di theen. aur hum ne un par kuch zulm nahikiya balkay wohi apne aap par zulm karte they
  16,119,phir jin logon ne nadani se bura kaamkiya. phir is ke baad tauba ki aur nekokaar hogaye to tumhara perwar-digaar ( un ko ) tauba karne aur nekokaar hojane ke baad bakhsnay wala aur un par rehmat karne wala hai
  16,120,be shak ibrahim ( logon ke ) imam aur khuda ke farmanbardar they. jo aik taraf ke ho rahay they aur mushrikon mein se nah they
  16,121,is ki nematon ke shukar guzar they. khuda ne un ko bargzidakiya tha aur ( apni ) seedhi raah par chalaya tha
  16,122,aur hum ne un ko duniya mein bhi khoobi di thi. aur woh akhirat mein bhi naik logon mein hon ge
  16,123,phir hum ne tumhari taraf wahi bhaije ke deen ibrahim ki pairwi ikhtiyar karo jo aik taraf ke ho rahay they aur mushrikon mein se nah they
  16,124,haftay ka din to un hi logon ke liye muqarrarkiya gaya tha. jinhon ne is mein ikhtilaafkiya. aur tumhara perwar-digaar qayamat ke din un mein un baton ka faisla kardey ga jin mein woh ikhtilaaf karte they
  16,125,( ae paighambar ) logon ko Danish aur naik nasiyaat se apne perwar-digaar ke raste ki taraf bulaao. aur bohat hi achay tareeq se un se manazra karo. jo is ke raste se bhatak gaya tumhara perwar-digaar usay bhi khoob jaanta hai aur jo raste par chalne walay hain un se bhi khoob waaqif hai
  16,126,aur agar tum un ko takleef dainee chaho to itni hi do jitni takleef tum ko un se pohanchi. aur agar sabr karo to woh sabr karne walon ke liye bohat acha hai
  16,127,aur sabr hi karo aur tumhara sabr bhi khuda hi ki madad se hai aur un ke baray mein gham nah karo aur jo yeh badandeshi karte hain is se tangdil nah ho
  16,128,kuch shak nahi ke jo parhaizgaar hain aur jo nekokaar hain khuda un ka madadgaar hai
